  <summary date="2020-03-31T15:25:36Z" status="Introduced in House">Survivors' Bill of Rights in the States Act of 2019

This bill directs the Department of Justice to make grants to states that provide certain legal rights to survivors of sexual assault. Among other things, grants may be used to implement such legal rights.</summary>
